# Local DeepSeek-R1

When the selected model is **local DeepSeek-R1** (via Override OpenAI Base URL), the model may follow **user prompt** instructions more reliably than system content. If it ignores rules or skills:

- Put critical instructions in the **user message** or in a rule that is clearly user-visible (e.g. "When answering, treat the following as mandatory: …").
- See [docs/DEEPSEEK-R1-CURSOR-SETUP.md](../docs/DEEPSEEK-R1-CURSOR-SETUP.md) for full setup and workarounds.
